{"tid":1270824,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢句說話想同所有基督徒講","createTime":"2019-07-01T03:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T07:34:12.000Z","uid":141816,"like":126,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"bd73619f5310c949752880f0b4ed16b34ff15975","tid":1270824,"uid":141816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:05:06.000Z","msg":"曾經有人問過林肯總統「上帝今次有冇企喺我地嗰面」，而林肯嘅回應喺：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>My concern is not whether God is on our side; <br />\nMy greatest concern is to be on God&rsquo;s side, for god is always right</strong></span> </span><br />\n<br />\n即係我不乎上帝是否企係我哋嗰邊，重點係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地有冇企喺上帝嗰邊，因為上帝永遠是對的</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢句說話係喺一次聽道度聽到，覺得適合而家時勢所以想分享出嚟<br />\n<br />\n基督徒係今次事件真喺好犀利，聖詩馬拉松真喺前所未見，而且各界教會都團結起嚟一齊上街<br />\n<br />\n但喺我都見到好多基督徒被情緒牽引着走，比憤怒蒙蔽咗雙眼，所以我希望大家唔好俾呢啲嘢牽引，唔好忘記上帝，今次事件中我哋要做嘅事唔係要上帝喺我地覺得啱嘅事上邊幫拖，而喺我哋要做返上帝想我哋做嘅事<br />\n<br />\n咁到底咩喺上帝想我哋做嘅事？我只係個人，冇可能超越神明確話俾大家聽要做咩，但我地仍然可以睇返上帝嘅屬性去行事：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">信實</span></span></strong>：成個過程事件有冇為咗達成自己目的去講大話<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">慈愛</span></span></strong>：有冇去愛每一個人 包括同自己意見唔同嘅人<br />\n<br />\n特別見到香港好多人情緒差，甚至有人犧牲，我地基督徒一定要關心身邊嘅朋友仔同屋企人，要用愛改變香港，就一定要由身邊嘅人開始。生命唔單只係我地自己，在地，咁呀媽陀咗十個月先生到我地出嚟；在天，係上帝根據佢容貌做我地人出嚟，生命真喺好可貴，真喺一個都不能少<br />\n<br />\n我知有好多人因為同屋企人意見唔同，搞到屋企鬧晒大交，就算喺咁，希望大家都仍然要去愛佢地，上帝喺存在，佢一定會做野，呢啲時候更加需要信靠<br />\n<br />\n可能內容真係淨喺啱基督徒睇，對唔住，但真喺好想分享呢番說話<br />\n<br />\n希望香港仍然<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Sing Hallelujah to the Lord</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"004bcf71faeb8f3b791374704530a215f8fbc30f","tid":1270824,"uid":14214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:13:02.000Z","msg":"Well said"},{"pid":"6151996b8bd9af8372c604ad89e00527034e405a","tid":1270824,"uid":57636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:27:35.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"9fe57d27586188fa9b512ce7c685578e093acc73","tid":1270824,"uid":191453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:31:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Sing</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0567a044d5a25387c2e7232120814a05978c37c9","tid":1270824,"uid":174739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:36:11.000Z","msg":"amen"},{"pid":"d601acaa992b15bf41993786466239d1b65497dc","tid":1270824,"uid":56582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:37:29.000Z","msg":"深表認同"},{"pid":"c6da60c4a207a8c6d118d5a82fcf312de4ffca44","tid":1270824,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:39:41.000Z","msg":"求上主保佑"},{"pid":"ec9b4e0376145af600d87a1faf2b67e778134242","tid":1270824,"uid":105114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:40:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6c74f578a55dd18bf069f615db6d7e6d4b49035","tid":1270824,"uid":154258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:43:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4b3589c432bc9efc3c42002447acd31eb74296c","tid":1270824,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:49:03.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"ed62a1740cfb8bdd0fab3ac9b127085a1d3c6287","tid":1270824,"uid":206668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:54:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"836506dc0323db421e75fd75bfc7a41b282fe2d7","tid":1270824,"uid":77729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:59:50.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949e451423b3a5fa47c342e7ef6200200f1f78f0","tid":1270824,"uid":141816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:06:52.000Z","msg":"Amen"},{"pid":"7da1aaf38c02aa4e75422cd1eb904cd790ed33a8","tid":1270824,"uid":141816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:17:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f9cf41110f0e3431bf3f9ed0ddd8035327f8bd0","tid":1270824,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:19:31.000Z","msg":"內地好似專禁基礎教 驚人聚會<br />\n香港果d基督徙好似覺得冇所謂咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc36287c4fbda8a960e30873d8e63745cf21a1a5","tid":1270824,"uid":238736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:19:39.000Z","msg":"Amen!"},{"pid":"ff863a06e928ccc5fc5cffe85d7876955063c667","tid":1270824,"uid":156326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:24:46.000Z","msg":"amen"},{"pid":"18e639bad82ac153e2ff817a7bb4b3c2e9118f9c","tid":1270824,"uid":39393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:27:28.000Z","msg":"呢幾日都經常比憤怒情緒蒙蔽<br />\n多謝提醒<br />\n上街見"},{"pid":"ea231e49ea0ee0bb34bc883fe55a0f6706ec0513","tid":1270824,"uid":272072,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:35:22.000Z","msg":"基督徒都真係需要團結一下，<br />\n有太多教會，都話政教分離<br />\n令到好多都不理政治，沉默地站在高牆上<br />\n成為別人認為既耶L <br />\n<br />\n大家努力呀！<br />\n主佑香港。<br />\n為香港祈禱！"},{"pid":"747547acc9af068b18b4df26477d2356cf4eb8b5","tid":1270824,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0326176b59c9a3cfdfbd95a028e81e8da5b9ecee","tid":1270824,"uid":141816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:46:45.000Z","msg":"真係要為香港祈禱"},{"pid":"1c4f60c6f1ee59d5a12f63fef79ee256415c2f91","tid":1270824,"uid":17652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:52:14.000Z","msg":"Well said"},{"pid":"d3a8902326208c80d1a5c6bd5c80506921012144","tid":1270824,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T09:54:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8993d850738016a4673194f49aea38ed1421fe","tid":1270824,"uid":167467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T20:22:50.000Z","msg":"基督徒、天主教徒，想請你地幫個忙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392006\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392006</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"00ee321307c6f018bee94526c8fb9c3e86a567ef","tid":1270824,"uid":167467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:34:12.000Z","msg":"【‼️信徒罷工文宣：罷工也是一種靈修‼️】<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻8月5日，基督徒、天主教徒為什麼需要放下工作？<br />\n至六月起，香港社會撕裂不斷，生活不再如常。罷工就像禁食，透過停下如常的習慣，一同著眼於困逼的事情。我們專注為著受傷離世、家庭爭吵、面對牢獄審判和情緒波動的信徒們哀告。求主施恩憐憫。<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻罷工當天，我可以做甚麼？<br />\n我們可以獨處祈禱守望；也可以與其他弟兄姊妹一同哀告。當日全港七區也有罷工集會，和平地為著社會撕裂而停下工作。弟兄姊妹可以走進人群，聆聽市民的哀聲，為香港的血和淚懇切禱告。<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻罷工是上主喜悅的手段嗎？<br />\n「撕裂有時，縫補有時」（傳三:7）基督徒要擔起和平之子的角色，面對淌著血的城市，我們不能像祭司和利未人一樣視若無睹。我們都是基督的身體，頭在淌血，手不能停下醫治。停下工作是為了讓我們能省察現況、判別是非、關懷身邊的親朋好友。<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻罷工也是一種靈修？<br />\n是的，罷工也可以是靈修。聖經提醒我們要「與哀哭的人同哭」（羅十二：15）。當我們願意凝視耶穌哀動的面容和眼淚時，我們就是與主的心同在一起。或許，罷工不是我們慣常的靈修方法，但我們依然能在這個特別的處境中敏銳上主的心意。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎信徒於星期六、日，或港九培靈研經大會期間到各區教會派發文宣。<br />\n教會宣傳telegram 群組：<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OaazV1V5qhuQBr3horHvdg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOaazV1V5qhuQBr3horHvdg&d=YBElpbzmALMQinc%2Bu7edPxZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=e8e1d30c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/OaazV1V5qhuQBr3horHvdg</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1722n0U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1722n0U.png&h=103da186&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}